### Get All Activities (No filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities

###

### Get Single Activity by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities/activity_123

###

### Get Activity Media
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities/activity_123/media

###

### Get Activities with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities?page=1&limit=5

###

### Filter Activities by Location
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities?location=Cape Town

###

### Filter Activities by Price Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities?minPrice=50&maxPrice=200

###

### Filter Activities by Location and Price Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities?location=Cape&minPrice=100&maxPrice=500

###

### Get Second Page with Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities?page=2&limit=10&location=Cape Town
###

### Get Activity Reviews
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities/activity_123/reviews

###

### Get Activity Reviews with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/activities/activity_123/reviews?page=1&limit=5

###